snippet.title: Outdoor leadership kids show
snippet.description:
Derek and I created this video for the final project in our outdoor leadership class taught by Karen Warren at Hampshire College. 

Our aim was to create a children’s TV show that would help kids get outside and see the importance of the outdoors in a funny light hearted way. 

The process of creation for this video was very light hearted, spontaneous and improvisational. We were able to draw on each other’s strengths and play with ideas. Because of our approach in playfully creating this video the project did not seem like work, it was a very fun activity that we both were exited to work on. 

I think this is a good example of the power of play to create. We both had a blast and used playful mindsets to accomplish a final project that was more then just another paper but instead a fun experience as well as a final product that many people can enjoy!

snippet.title: Carry On™ Multi-Pocket Carrier 8-40 lbs Unboxing/Testing  |  Lynley's World
snippet.description:
Unboxing this carry on multi-pocket carrier for my toddler. It has 6 organized pockets, adjustable seat, adjustable head support and outward-stretch expandable pockets for diapers, wipes & outfits. 4 carrying positions. 3.6-18.1 kgs. 

Planned on doing a 10-minute outdoor walk to test it but I couldn't do it.

snippet.title: BLEU! - Interactive dance and theatre for children
snippet.description:
compagnia TPO in co-production with

Teatro Metastasio Stabile della Toscana 
Théâtre Joliette Minoterie 
Marseille-Provence 2013, Capitale européenne de la culture
 
artistic direction Francesco Gandi, Davide Venturini
choreography Anna Balducci
dance for two performers
visual environment Elsa Mersi
sound environment Spartaco Cortesi
computer programming and interactive systems Rossano Monti
costumes Fiamma Ciotti Farulli
props Livia Cortesi
organization Valentina Martini, Francesca Nunziati, Chiara Saponari

Borrowing from classical mythology and from stories that compose the very Mediterranean area itself, Bleu! narrates the meeting of two characters: a Sailor and a magical and mysterious being who is a Sea Nymph. It all starts when "She" drops a pearl into the sea so that "He" can find it. The sailor will have to undertake an adventurous journey, plowing the sea waters and diving to the lowest abysses, transforming the story into an active discovery and search for knowledge.
Stars are the guiding presence in Bleu! and they serve to transversely unite one stage scene to another, giving viewers firm reference points in the story. Indeed by following the paths of the stars, we will face stormy waters and howling winds; we will meet some sea dwellers; we will dance, play music, and create moments of play for a small, close-knit crew.
In Bleu! the natural elements of the marine environment become the setting of a virtual journey undertaken by actors and audience alike. The centrally situated stage is floored with a large dance carpet; on this surface are projected images evoking a beach where small treasures have washed ashore and are ready for the taking. Above the stage hangs a large and mobile spiral structure made of tulle fabric; in constant and slow transformation, its surfaces become the screen for projections which allow images to float in mid-air, making the space an even more totally immersive experience.

In this setting small groups of children will interact with the two dancers and the "found" objects, as well as with the play's images and sounds, in a process of unveiling the secret life of the marine environment.

snippet.title: Best budget hotel for Disneyland Florida? Embassy Suites Lake Buena Vista Orlando Virgin Holidays
snippet.description:
If this video helps, LEAVE A COMMENT below to say hi - I'd love to hear from you.
You can also help me by clicking THUMBS UP or get to 1000 subscribers with SUBSCRIBE here thanks! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC5GL2M_HNyaLy_kEQwVp0KQ?sub_confirmation=1

SHOT SEPTEMBER 1, 2017
What does a Virgin Holidays Orlando, Embassy Suites by Hilton Lake Buena Vista hotel room look like?  Here's our review.
We loved this hotel and had a great time there - we didn't say it in the video because we'd just arrived.  

The video shows a standard hotel room, the pool area, outdoor bar, and other facilities and an attempt to explain how the hotel's shuttle buses work.  (After our visit, we're still not sure how they work... they mostly arrived - we used Uber as a backup, but that was fraught with mobile phone data and even getting reception when you need it most)  It was great! #Orlando #LakeBuenaVista
Thanks for watching

snippet.title: ВИДЕО ДЛЯ ДЕТЕЙ про Детские Площадки Funny Outdoor Playgrounds for kids
snippet.description:
ВИДЕО ДЛЯ ДЕТЕЙ про детские развлечения и детские игровые площадки. VIDEO FOR CHILDREN about the outdoor playgrounds. 遊び場 . 子供の遊び場 . 遊び場 子供の遊び場

Эдгар играет на детской игровой площадке, качается на машинках - качалках на пружине, лазит в лабиринте, спускается с горок в виде вертолета, машины, поезда и корабля, играет в игровом комплексе в виде здания Кремля в Москве.

Детские игровые комплексы играют большую роль в физическом развитии детей – на детской площадке ребенок в веселой игровой форме получает физические нагрузки на все группы мышц на свежем воздухе, что способствует физическому развитию ребенка, а игры на детской площадке в коллективе развивают социальные навыки детей.

ВИДЕО ДЛЯ ДЕТЕЙ про детские развлечения и детские игровые площадки. VIDEO FOR CHILDREN about the outdoor playgrounds. 遊び場 . 子供の遊び場 . 遊び場 子供の遊び場

Эдгар играет на детской игровой площадке, качается на машинках - качалках на пружине, лазит в лабиринте, спускается с горок в виде вертолета, машины, поезда и корабля, играет в игровом комплексе в виде здания Кремля в Москве.

Детские игровые комплексы играют большую роль в физическом развитии детей – на детской площадке ребенок в веселой игровой форме получает физические нагрузки на все группы мышц на свежем воздухе, что способствует физическому развитию ребенка, а игры на детской площадке в коллективе развивают социальные навыки детей.

snippet.title: The importance of outdoor play for kids
snippet.description: The natural habit for children is outdoor play, not sitting in from of a video game or other electronic device.  In this video I give you an example of the street where I live and how I encourage outdoor play for my kids and the neighbors kids.  Together let's unplug America.

snippet.title: Baby Play Fun Gardening | Outdoor play activity for Kids
snippet.description:
Gardening is a very healthy activity that teaches kids about healthy living, eating organic and getting close to nature. It is a long term project that engages your kids to work patiently and with full dedication.

Make a kid-size garden for the little ones to handle easily. Start out with wild flowers. They are of various colors and are easily available in the market. They also look good in small colored pots.
